embeds.title: New Cards
embeds.description: We're thrilled to unveil the latest addition to our ever-expanding galaxy of cards: **Grand Moff Tarkin**! With his strategic brilliance and ruthless determination, Tarkin is here to leave his mark on the battlefield.

fields.name: <:tarki:1161753835962904597> Grand Moff Tarkin
fields.value: As the head of the Galactic Empire's military, Grand Moff Tarkin is a master tactician and a fearsome commander. His presence on the battlefield can turn the tide of any battle, but it also sends a chilling message to those who oppose the Empire. Will you use his cunning to dominate your foes, or will you challenge his authority and attempt to outwit him? The choice is yours!
